84
00:07:48,430 --> 00:07:50,830
你在哪里?快告诉我你的坐标
Where are you, soldier?I need your position.

85
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:53,090
- 我不知道 - 你能看见什么吗？
- I don't know. - What do you see?

86
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:56,790
什么也看不见 我们损失惨重 小队长也阵亡了
I can't see anything, sir. We lost a lot of men and captain is dead, sir.

87
00:07:56,790 --> 00:08:00,880
- 冷静 现在由你来指挥 - 我吗 长官
- Calm down. You're in command now. - Command, sir?

88
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:04,250
我觉得这只有我一个人了
I think it’s just me by myself now.

89
00:08:07,330 --> 00:08:09,890
上校 我大概没有活路了
Colonel, I don‘t think I'm gonna make it, sir.

90
00:08:09,890 --> 00:08:12,380
抱歉 长官 真的很抱歉
I am sorry. I am so sorry, sir.

91
00:08:12,380 --> 00:08:15,780
听我说 那你能杀多少就杀多少
Listen to me. Kill as many as you can.

92
00:08:19,770 --> 00:08:22,480
不 不 不！
No. No, no!

93
00:09:37,490 --> 00:09:40,430
阵亡63人
63 dead.

94
00:09:45,220 --> 00:09:48,680
就是你 你就是凯撒
You are him. You're Caesar.

95
00:09:49,970 --> 00:09:52,600
我们找你找得好苦
We've been searching for you for so long.

96
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:56,140
我们听说你有个隐蔽的指挥所 但我们就是找不到
We heard you had a hidden command base, but we could never find it.

97
00:09:56,140 --> 00:09:58,610
我们当中有些人 觉得你可能已经死了
Some of us were starting to think that you might be dead,

98
00:09:58,620 --> 00:10:01,310
但麦卡洛上校说你没死 而是藏在某处
but the Colonel McCullough said you were out here somewhere.

99
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:03,110
- 要杀就痛快点 - 闭嘴！
- Just kill us already. - Shut up, man!

100
00:10:03,110 --> 00:10:07,130
怎么了？它们就是一群畜生 它会宰了我们的
What? They're animals. He's gonna slaughter us.

101
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:19,400
这场战争不是我挑起的
I did not start this war.

102
00:10:19,530 --> 00:10:23,240
罪魁祸首已经死了
The ape who did is dead.

103
00:10:24,130 --> 00:10:26,470
他叫科巴
His name was Koba.

104
00:10:26,470 --> 00:10:29,180
我已经处决了他
I killed him.

105
00:10:30,730 --> 00:10:37,630
- 如今我只为保护猿族而战 - 是吗？
- Now I fight only to protect apes.  - Yeah?

106
00:10:39,190 --> 00:10:43,820
那他呢？我们还有十多个那样的猿族
What about him? We got ten more just like him.

107
00:10:44,310 --> 00:10:49,670
我认识他们 科巴的亲信
I know these apes. They followed Koba.

108
00:10:50,460 --> 00:10:52,950
他们曾想杀了我
They tried to kill me.

109
00:10:52,950 --> 00:10:56,440
他们害怕我的惩罚
They fear what I will do to them.

110
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:58,540
所以
So now

111
00:10:58,540 --> 00:11:01,120
现在他们跟着你们
they serve you?

112
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:03,830
只是为了活命
just to survive.

113
00:11:04,740 --> 00:11:08,590
我可不怕你
I no fear you!

114
00:11:11,700 --> 00:11:15,460
你才应该害怕
You must fear!

115
00:11:15,460 --> 00:11:19,830
你觉得你们还能在森林里藏多久？
How long you think woods can protect you?

116
00:11:19,830 --> 00:11:23,430
人类能毁了你
Humans destroy you.

117
00:11:23,910 --> 00:11:28,370
上校拥有至高无上的权力
Their Colonel has all power.

118
00:11:28,520 --> 00:11:33,490
对这些人来说 他可不是个普通人
For them, he more than just human.

119
00:11:35,210 --> 00:11:37,370
他就是神
He everything.

120
00:11:37,370 --> 00:11:41,440
他说 先杀了凯撒
He say: "First Caesar die?

121
00:11:42,340 --> 00:11:46,260
再让所有猴子给他陪葬
then all of you die."

122
00:11:52,490 --> 00:11:56,360
温特 把这个叛徒带走
Winter! Take this traitor outside!

123
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:06,100
怎么处理这些人类？
What should we do with the humans?

124
00:12:19,130 --> 00:12:21,280
你要放我们走？
You are letting us go?

125
00:12:21,280 --> 00:12:25,160
告诉这位上校 你们见到我了
Tell your Colonel, you have seen me now.

126
00:12:25,400 --> 00:12:29,490
替我传个话 只要他把森林留给我们
And I have a message for him. Leave us the woods?

127
00:12:29,490 --> 00:12:32,200
一切杀戮就可以结束了
and the killing can stop.

128
00:12:41,880 --> 00:12:45,820
你觉得他们会传话吗？
Do you think they will give him the message?

129
00:12:45,820 --> 00:12:49,000
他们本身就传达了我的意思 毛里斯
They are the message, Maurice.

130
00:12:49,040 --> 00:12:52,120
他会明白我们并不是什么野蛮动物
He will see we are not savages.

131
00:12:59,090 --> 00:13:03,660
那个叛徒攻击了我！他跑了！
The traitor attacked me! He got away!

132
00:13:30,160 --> 00:13:34,220
科巴真是阴魂不散
Koba still haunts us.

133
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:44,020
我之前没意识到 人类对他的所做所为 他有多么耿耿于怀
What I didn't see that he could not forgive what humans did to him.

134
00:13:44,590 --> 00:13:48,080
没人知道他内心
No one could have known how much darkness...

135
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:52,120
有多阴暗
was living inside him.

136
00:14:25,450 --> 00:14:28,690
父亲！
Father!

137
00:14:43,190 --> 00:14:45,500
欢迎回家 火箭
Welcome home, Rocket.

138
00:14:45,500 --> 00:14:48,150
你受累了
You look tired.

139
00:14:48,150 --> 00:14:52,910
- 路途遥远 - 父亲 我们有发现！
- It was a long journey. - Father, we found something!

140
00:14:52,910 --> 00:14:55,620
跟我来
Come.

141
00:15:20,580 --> 00:15:23,410
母亲
Mother!

142
00:15:30,370 --> 00:15:35,150
科尼利厄斯 快和你哥哥打个招呼
Cornelius... Say hi to your brother!

143
00:15:43,140 --> 00:15:46,180
儿子 快看这是谁
Look who's here, son...

144
00:15:56,020 --> 00:15:59,490
莱克
Lake...

145
00:16:27,850 --> 00:16:33,140
就是这里 父亲 我们可以在这里建个新家园 重新开始
This is it, Father. We can start over. A new home.

146
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:39,200
- 儿子 那些山的另一边是什么？ - 给他们看看 火箭
- What is beyond those mountains, son? - Show them, Rocket.

147
00:16:50,990 --> 00:16:55,310
一个沙漠！路途很遥远...
A desert! The journey is long...

148
00:16:55,310 --> 00:16:58,180
所以人类不会找上门来的
But that is why humans will not find us.

149
00:16:58,180 --> 00:17:01,190
我们必须今晚就离开！
We must leave tonight!

150
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:03,430
今晚？不可能
Tonight? That's impossible.

151
00:17:03,430 --> 00:17:09,090
- 我们还能躲多久 莱克？军队快来了！ - 温特…
- How long can we wait, Lake? Soldiers getting closer! - Winter...

152
00:17:17,070 --> 00:17:20,460
你儿子这段时间不在 凯撒...
Your son's been gone, Caesar...

153
00:17:20,460 --> 00:17:25,270
他不知道我们的生活多艰难
He doesn't know how hard it's been.

154
00:17:27,140 --> 00:17:30,540
我知道你很害怕
I know you are scared...

155
00:17:30,540 --> 00:17:33,180
我们都怕
We all are...

156
00:17:33,180 --> 00:17:37,020
但我们还是需要好好计划
But we are still planning...

157
00:17:38,650 --> 00:17:44,990
对 我们要找到离开森林的安全路线
Yes. We must find a safe way out of woods.

158
00:17:44,990 --> 00:17:47,420
之前只有你们俩
There were only two of you.

159
00:17:47,420 --> 00:17:51,430
但是我们有很多同胞
But we are many.

160
00:18:01,430 --> 00:18:05,540
我们会找到路线走出去的
We will find a way out of here.

161
00:18:07,620 --> 00:18:13,680
猿族要团结起来才能强大
Apes together strong.

162
00:19:22,300 --> 00:19:26,840
留在这 儿子 保护你妈妈和弟弟！
Stay here, son. Protect your mother and brother!

163
00:20:10,390 --> 00:20:12,390
凯撒！怎么了？
Caesar! What's wrong?

164
00:20:12,390 --> 00:20:14,230
有多少人在巡逻？
How many on patrol?

165
00:20:14,230 --> 00:20:17,050
- 五六个人？- 集结起来！
- Five? Six? - Get them!

166
00:20:17,050 --> 00:20:20,300
卢卡 叫上火箭
Luca, get Rocket too.

167
00:21:12,350 --> 00:21:15,290
呼叫指挥部 上校...
Unit calling command. Colonel...

168
00:21:24,630 --> 00:21:30,640
- 火箭？怎么了？- 我听见他说话了！上校在这里！
- Rocket? What happened? - I heard him talking! Colonel is here!

169
00:21:31,510 --> 00:21:34,540
九十九号 目标已拿下
Ninety-nine, target acquired.

170
00:21:34,540 --> 00:21:39,750
九十九号 目标已拿下 重复一遍 金刚已死
Ninety-nine, target acquired. Repeat, King Kong is dead.

171
00:21:39,750 --> 00:21:43,410
我们走吧 我要从这里上去
Let's go. I get up from here.

172
00:23:48,540 --> 00:23:53,050
凯撒... 我们找不到温特！
Caesar... We can't find Winter!

173
00:23:55,100 --> 00:23:59,730
他之前吓坏了！我觉得他背叛了我们！
He was scared! I think he betrayed us!

174
00:24:03,170 --> 00:24:07,460
你们找到科尼利厄斯了吗？
Have you found Cornelius yet?

175
00:24:07,460 --> 00:24:10,550
我们还在找
We're still searching.

176
00:24:14,210 --> 00:24:18,570
我们去找凯撒的小儿子吧
Let's go look for Caesar’s little son.

177
00:24:51,160 --> 00:24:54,160
过来 科尼利厄斯
Come, Cornelius.

178
00:25:01,660 --> 00:25:04,810
你已经安全了
You're safe now.

179
00:25:21,550 --> 00:25:23,800
莱克
Lake.

180
00:25:23,800 --> 00:25:26,150
既然你爱我的儿子
You loved my son.

181
00:25:26,150 --> 00:25:30,290
那就照顾好他的弟弟 等我回来
Look after his brother, until I return.

182
00:25:34,770 --> 00:25:38,910
你不和大家一起去我们的新家吗？
You're not coming with us to our new home?

183
00:25:38,910 --> 00:25:41,620
不
No.

184
00:25:44,560 --> 00:25:47,270
和莱克一起走
Go with Lake.

185
00:26:02,010 --> 00:26:06,610
凯撒！你不是要去追他们吧?!
Caesar! You're not going after them?!

186
00:26:07,920 --> 00:26:09,640
不是他们 是他
Not them, him.

187
00:26:09,640 --> 00:26:13,810
凯撒 你是我们的首领！
Caesar, you are our leader!

188
00:26:13,810 --> 00:26:17,550
我们不能没有首领自己走！
We can't leave without you!

189
00:26:17,690 --> 00:26:20,250
必须这样
You must.

190
00:26:20,250 --> 00:26:22,390
士兵们很快就会回来
The soldiers will be back soon.

191
00:26:22,390 --> 00:26:25,340
爸爸！
Father!

192
00:26:25,950 --> 00:26:30,400
等我找到他 所有士兵都会来追我
When I find him, the soldiers will all come after me.

193
00:26:31,060 --> 00:26:35,050
那是你们离开森林的最好机会了
That makes you the best chance to get out of woods.

194
00:26:37,440 --> 00:26:40,590
他去哪？！
Where is he going?!

195
00:26:43,300 --> 00:26:47,820
凯撒！凯撒！
Caesar! Caesar!

196
00:27:35,820 --> 00:27:38,330
那些士兵的营地总是不固定
The soldiers' camp is always moving.

197
00:27:38,360 --> 00:27:41,000
我的卫兵们知道在哪能找到营地
My guards think they know where it is.

198
00:27:41,000 --> 00:27:46,060
- 让我一起去 - 你需要我帮助你！
- Let me take you. - You need me to back you up!

199
00:27:46,210 --> 00:27:48,740
不！
No!

200
00:27:48,740 --> 00:27:56,290
拜托了... 我知道失去儿子的感受
Please... I know what it's like to lose a son.

201
00:27:56,710 --> 00:28:01,120
我可能回不来了
I may not make it back.

202
00:28:01,340 --> 00:28:05,730
所以我才要一起去
That's why I'm coming.

203
00:28:06,350 --> 00:28:10,200
好让你可以回来
To make sure you do.

204
00:28:45,780 --> 00:28:51,790
卫兵们觉得那些士兵在这里... 这里一直点着火
Guards think soldiers here... Always fires burning.

205
00:29:04,110 --> 00:29:06,550
这里没有人
No one here.

206
00:29:06,550 --> 00:29:09,750
搜索这片区域
Search the area.

207
00:29:31,810 --> 00:29:34,710
先让我把这些放下
Just gonna put this down.

208
00:30:08,050 --> 00:30:10,700
他一个人在这里干什么？
What's he doing out here alone?

209
00:30:10,710 --> 00:30:13,910
也许他是个逃兵？
Maybe he's a deserter?

210
00:31:25,340 --> 00:31:28,050
四处看看
Look around.

211
00:31:30,230 --> 00:31:32,940
能拿的东西都尽量带走
Take what you can.

212
00:33:25,770 --> 00:33:30,780
她有点不对劲 我觉得她不会说话
Something wrong with her. I don't think she can speak.

213
00:33:31,750 --> 00:33:34,460
走吧
Come.

214
00:33:51,410 --> 00:33:56,210
她自己一个人活不下去
She'll die out here alone.

215
00:33:56,780 --> 00:34:00,000
我们不能带她走 毛里斯
We cannot take her, Maurice.

216
00:34:03,150 --> 00:34:09,530
我明白... 但是我不能就这么扔下她
I understand... But I cannot leave her.

