01:10:23,590 --> 01:10:26,340
- 教训他 – 好的
- Get him! - Okay, okay.

439
01:10:26,340 --> 01:10:29,050
好的
Okay.

440
01:10:56,540 --> 01:10:59,250
别再打了！
Leave him!

441
01:13:37,040 --> 01:13:43,670
- 让他们回去继续工作 – 我们需要食物和水
- Tell them to get back to work. - Apes need food and water.

442
01:13:45,660 --> 01:13:51,200
- 告诉他们 – 给他们食物和水
- Tell them. - Give them food and water.

443
01:13:59,080 --> 01:14:01,200
五
Five.

444
01:14:01,200 --> 01:14:03,750
四
Four.

445
01:14:03,750 --> 01:14:06,460
三
Three.

446
01:14:06,860 --> 01:14:09,570
二
Two.

447
01:14:25,420 --> 01:14:29,760
快回去工作！
Hurry! Back to work!

448
01:14:46,280 --> 01:14:49,100
把他绑起来 驴子
String him up, donkey.

449
01:14:58,190 --> 01:15:01,270
坏地方
Bad place.

450
01:15:02,490 --> 01:15:05,330
很坏 很坏的地方
Bad, bad place.

451
01:15:07,350 --> 01:15:10,060
你看到了什么
What you see?

452
01:15:15,230 --> 01:15:18,230
- 一定要救他们 – 怎么救？
- Must save them! - But how?

453
01:15:18,260 --> 01:15:22,070
动动脑子 凯撒他会怎么做？
Must think! What would Caesar do?

454
01:15:22,910 --> 01:15:25,620
啊！
No!

455
01:15:27,040 --> 01:15:29,750
怎么这么小？
Why so small?

456
01:16:01,480 --> 01:16:04,220
上校承诺了你什么？
What did the Colonel promised you?

457
01:16:04,220 --> 01:16:08,380
你真以为他会放过你吗
You really think he let you live?

458
01:16:08,380 --> 01:16:11,090
在我们都死了之后？
After we are gone?

459
01:16:11,260 --> 01:16:14,430
你让他们叫你驴子
You let them call you donkey.

460
01:16:14,430 --> 01:16:17,220
可你是猿类
You are ape.

461
01:16:25,890 --> 01:16:29,500
上校要见你
Colonel wants see you.

462
01:16:47,430 --> 01:16:48,630
历史

463
01:16:53,290 --> 01:16:55,070
再敢妨碍他们干活
Interfere with the work again,

464
01:16:55,100 --> 01:16:57,820
我就把他们一个个全都杀掉
I will begin slaughtering the apes, one by one.

465
01:16:57,820 --> 01:17:00,060
听懂了吗？我需要那堵墙
Understand? I need that wall.

466
01:17:00,060 --> 01:17:02,320
他们需要食物和水
Apes need food and water.

467
01:17:02,350 --> 01:17:07,420
当任务完成后 我自然会给他们食物和水
They'll get food and water when they finish their work.

468
01:17:09,080 --> 01:17:12,010
给他们食物和水
Give apes food and water.

469
01:17:12,010 --> 01:17:16,740
- 否则任务没法完成 – 你太感情用事了
- Or they cannot finish it. - You know, you're very emotional.

470
01:17:18,450 --> 01:17:23,280
你有什么资本跟我讨价还价？
What makes you think you’re in a position to make demands?

471
01:17:27,700 --> 01:17:31,060
- 好了 我们走 – 大部队快到了
- Okay, let's go. - The soldiers who are coming here,

472
01:17:31,060 --> 01:17:35,330
他们不是来和你汇合的 对吧？
they are not coming to join you, are they?

473
01:17:35,720 --> 01:17:41,560
我看到外面那些士兵 在墙上准备作战
I saw men outside, on the wall, preparing for battle.

474
01:17:43,170 --> 01:17:47,980
他们告诉我你很聪明 不过想不到这么聪明
They told me you're smart, but that's impressive.

475
01:17:47,980 --> 01:17:51,730
对 他们不是来汇合的
No, they won't be joining me.

476
01:17:51,730 --> 01:17:53,440
他们是你的敌人吗？
They are against you?

477
01:17:53,440 --> 01:17:56,590
他们害怕我
They fear me.

478
01:17:56,590 --> 01:18:00,750
为什么 因为你连自己人也杀吗？
Why? Because you kill your own men?

479
01:18:01,190 --> 01:18:03,500
我们发现了尸体
We found bodies.

480
01:18:03,500 --> 01:18:07,890
那几个人很不对劲
Something wrong with these men.

481
01:18:10,140 --> 01:18:13,940
天哪 你真是让我大开眼界
Jesus Christ, you are impressive.

482
01:18:15,030 --> 01:18:19,260
据你所知 你肯定觉得我不是好人
You paint quite a picture. What you must think of me.

483
01:18:19,560 --> 01:18:23,060
我觉得你没有怜悯之心
I think you have no mercy.

484
01:18:40,730 --> 01:18:43,440
你可是来杀我的
You came here to kill me.

485
01:18:44,070 --> 01:18:46,050
难道你会对我有怜悯之心吗？
Were you going to show me mercy?

486
01:18:46,060 --> 01:18:50,820
我放了你的人 这就是我的怜悯之心
I showed you mercy when I spared your men.

487
01:18:50,820 --> 01:18:55,940
我提出了和平共处 可你却杀了我的家人
I offered you peace and you killed my family.

488
01:19:10,230 --> 01:19:12,570
怜悯
Mercy.

489
01:19:12,580 --> 01:19:16,830
你知道你的怜悯会让我们陷入怎样的境地吗？
Do you have any idea what your mercy would do to us?

490
01:19:19,890 --> 01:19:22,850
你们比我们强壮
You’re much stronger than we are.

491
01:19:23,070 --> 01:19:25,310
还那么聪明
You're smart as hell.

492
01:19:25,320 --> 01:19:28,870
不管你怎么说 你们终将取代我们
No matter what you say, you’d eventually replace us.

493
01:19:28,900 --> 01:19:30,710
这是自然的法则
That’s the law of Nature.

494
01:19:30,840 --> 01:19:32,980
讽刺的是 是我们创造了你们
The irony is, we created you.

495
01:19:32,980 --> 01:19:36,110
我们总是试着违背自然 征服自然
We tried to defy Nature, bend it to our will.

496
01:19:36,110 --> 01:19:41,420
于是大自然开始惩罚我们的自以为是
And Nature’s been punishing us for our arrogance ever since.

497
01:19:43,650 --> 01:19:47,130
十个月前 我派出了侦查小组去寻找你们的基地
Ten months ago, I sent out recon units to look for your base.

498
01:19:47,130 --> 01:19:50,770
我的儿子就是这个小组的一员
My own son was a soldier with one of the units.

499
01:19:50,770 --> 01:19:53,060
有一天他突然不能说话了
One day he suddenly stopped speaking.

500
01:19:53,060 --> 01:19:55,700
他变得原始化 像动物一样
He became primitive, like an animal.

501
01:19:55,700 --> 01:19:57,040
他们告诉我
They contacted me,

502
01:19:57,070 --> 01:20:00,200
说他们觉得我儿子疯了
said that they thought he’d lost his mind,

503
01:20:00,310 --> 01:20:03,330
因为承受不住战争的压力
that the war was too much for him.

504
01:20:03,500 --> 01:20:07,520
后来负责照顾他的那个人也不会说话了
Then the man who cared for him stopped speaking too.

505
01:20:07,870 --> 01:20:12,540
在小队的医务兵还能说话的时候 他提出了一个理论
Their medic had a theory, before he stopped speaking,

506
01:20:12,550 --> 01:20:15,210
即使是幸存者身上也同样携带着
that the virus that almost wiped us out,

507
01:20:15,210 --> 01:20:19,590
那让人类濒临灭绝的可怕病毒
the virus that every human survivor still carries,

508
01:20:19,590 --> 01:20:21,900
病毒突变了
had suddenly changed.

509
01:20:21,900 --> 01:20:24,610
变异了
Mutated.

510
01:20:24,980 --> 01:20:30,420
如果它转播开来 人类将会彻底灭亡
And if it spread, it would destroy humanity for good this time.

511
01:20:31,700 --> 01:20:37,350
不是杀死我们 而是会夺走我们之所以成为人类的核心
Not by killing us, but by robbing us of the things that make us human.

512
01:20:37,350 --> 01:20:40,130
我们的语言 我们的高等思想
Our speech, our higher thinking.

513
01:20:40,130 --> 01:20:44,980
它会把我们变成野兽 而你却在这儿跟我谈怜悯？
It would turn us into beasts. You talk about mercy?

514
01:20:46,810 --> 01:20:49,520
换作你你会怎么做？
What would you have done?

515
01:20:51,630 --> 01:20:54,520
当时有那么一刻我非常清醒
It was a moment of clarity for me.

516
01:20:54,520 --> 01:20:58,750
我意识到我必须牺牲自己唯一的儿子
I realized that I would have to sacrifice my only son,

517
01:20:58,750 --> 01:21:02,710
这样人类才能得以保全
so that humanity could be saved.

518
01:21:04,740 --> 01:21:10,300
我握着那把枪很久很久
I held that gun in my hand for a long time...

519
01:21:13,900 --> 01:21:19,050
我把它对着我唯一的孩子
And I pointed it at my only child.

520
01:21:20,480 --> 01:21:26,480
他看着我 眼神里全是信任
He looked at me with trust in his eyes.

521
01:21:28,210 --> 01:21:31,390
即使在他原始的眼神中
Even in his primitive gaze,

522
01:21:35,560 --> 01:21:38,290
我也感受到了他的…
I felt his...

523
01:21:38,340 --> 01:21:41,050
爱
love.

524
01:21:46,720 --> 01:21:49,840
我扣动了扳机
I pulled the trigger.

525
01:21:50,850 --> 01:21:56,950
我感觉被净化了 这使我的目标更加明确
It purified me. It made my purpose clear.

526
01:21:58,350 --> 01:22:02,540
我下令杀掉其他所有被感染的人
I gave orders to kill the others infected, all of them.

527
01:22:02,540 --> 01:22:07,420
烧掉他们任何能够传播病毒的东西
Burn their belongings, anything that might spread contamination.

528
01:22:07,420 --> 01:22:09,950
有些手下质疑我的判断
Some of the men questioned my judgment.

529
01:22:09,950 --> 01:22:13,070
我是在让他们去做和我一样的选择
I was asking them to do what I had done,

530
01:22:13,070 --> 01:22:19,000
牺牲他们的朋友 家人
to sacrifice their friends, their family.

531
01:22:20,710 --> 01:22:23,940
当然 他们拒绝了
Of course, they refused.

532
01:22:25,970 --> 01:22:28,680
所以我把他们也杀了
I had them killed too.

533
01:22:29,850 --> 01:22:35,070
其他带着孩子的偷偷逃进了树林里
Others with children deserted into the woods.

534
01:22:35,560 --> 01:22:39,570
有一个懦夫 跑到了北方我的上级那里
One of those cowards fled to my superiors up north.

535
01:22:39,570 --> 01:22:41,440
他们试图说服我
They tried to convince me

536
01:22:41,470 --> 01:22:44,910
让我相信这场瘟疫可以通过医疗手段来解决
that this plague could be dealt with medically.

537
01:22:44,910 --> 01:22:51,600
我意识到 在经历了这么多之后他们还是什么都没学到
That’s when I realized that they had learned nothing from our past.

538
01:22:52,860 --> 01:22:55,830
你把他们也杀了？
You killed them too?

539
01:22:57,100 --> 01:22:59,810
我是怎么做的来着 普里彻？
What did I do, Preacher?

540
01:23:00,250 --> 01:23:02,890
你砍下了他们的脑袋 长官
You severed their heads, sir.

541
01:23:02,890 --> 01:23:05,250
除了被我放走的那一个
Except for the one I spared

542
01:23:05,250 --> 01:23:08,360
我让他回去替我捎个口信
so he could return and deliver a message.

543
01:23:08,360 --> 01:23:11,170
如果他们想要卸下我的指挥权
If they wanted to relieve me of my command,

544
01:23:11,170 --> 01:23:15,770
就得来这里找我 亲自动手
they’d have to meet me here, and do it themselves.

545
01:23:15,770 --> 01:23:18,580
这里曾经是个军械库
This used to be a weapons depot.

546
01:23:18,630 --> 01:23:23,410
在猿流感爆发初期 他们把这里改造成了一个集中营
They turned it into a relocation camp when the crisis was just beginning.

547
01:23:23,900 --> 01:23:28,290
但是武器还在这里 就在山里面
But the weapons are all still here, inside the mountain.

548
01:23:28,290 --> 01:23:31,790
他们会派多少人来？
How many men will be coming?

549
01:23:31,790 --> 01:23:33,500
可能会倾巢出动
Probably all of them.

550
01:23:33,500 --> 01:23:35,560
但别想太多
But don’t get any ideas,

551
01:23:35,560 --> 01:23:39,010
除了我 他们最怕的就是你们猿类了
the only thing they fear more than me is you apes.

552
01:23:45,550 --> 01:23:50,210
这是一场圣战
This is a holy war.

553
01:23:51,090 --> 01:23:55,590
所有人类历史都指向这一时刻
All of human history has led to this moment.

554
01:23:55,590 --> 01:24:00,590
如果我们输了 我们将成为最后的人类
If we lose, we’II be the last of our kind.

555
01:24:00,850 --> 01:24:07,620
我们的地球会成为你们的猩球 而我们也会成为你们的牲口
It will be a planet of apes, and we’II become your cattle.

556
01:24:08,610 --> 01:24:11,320
看看你
Look at you.

557
01:24:11,320 --> 01:24:14,150
你觉得我疯了 对吧？
You think I am sick, don't you?

558
01:24:22,220 --> 01:24:25,190
我其实并不想杀你儿子
I didn’t mean to kill your son.

559
01:24:26,810 --> 01:24:31,440
但如果他注定会继承你的王位
But if his destiny was to inherit your unholy kingdom...

560
01:24:32,470 --> 01:24:35,180
那我很欣慰我杀了他
I am glad I did.

561
01:24:36,670 --> 01:24:39,380
回来！
Get back!

562
01:24:47,170 --> 01:24:49,880
这么感情用事！
So emotional!

563
01:24:56,500 --> 01:24:59,390
我知道你内心非常纠结
I see how conflicted you are.

564
01:24:59,700 --> 01:25:03,100
你搞不清楚自己的目标
You are confused in your purpose.

565
01:25:03,230 --> 01:25:08,450
你对我的所作所为感到愤怒 但这就是残酷的战争
You’re angry at me for something I did that was an act of war.

566
01:25:08,630 --> 01:25:13,120
而现在你已经对此注入了太多的私人恩怨
But you’re taking this all much far too personally.

567
01:25:14,960 --> 01:25:19,880
你好好想想 如果你杀了我
What do you think my men would have done to your apes,

568
01:25:19,880 --> 01:25:22,670
我的人会怎么处置你的同类？
if you had killed me?

569
01:25:23,150 --> 01:25:25,910
还是说杀了我对你来说更重要？
Or is killing me more important?

570
01:25:37,920 --> 01:25:42,520
到处都是士兵 我们要怎么进去？
Soldiers everywhere! How will we get in?

571
01:25:42,840 --> 01:25:47,660
得想办法进去 必须得进去！
Must get in somehow... Must get in!

572
01:25:48,760 --> 01:25:51,080
进去？要进去？
In? In?

573
01:25:51,080 --> 01:25:52,980
不行！
No!

574
01:25:52,980 --> 01:25:56,130
不能进去！不能！
No go in! No!

575
01:26:02,960 --> 01:26:06,630
朋友 朋友！不能进去！
Friends! Friends! No! No go in!

576
01:26:06,630 --> 01:26:09,340
不能进去！
No go in!

577
01:26:11,460 --> 01:26:14,480
朋友！朋友！
Friend! Friend!

578
01:26:17,820 --> 01:26:21,030
谢谢 谢谢 朋友
Thank you. Thank you, friend.

579
01:27:06,370 --> 01:27:09,780
你救了我们的命！
You save our lives!

580
01:27:46,230 --> 01:27:53,930
此路

581
01:27:46,230 --> 01:27:53,930
可逃出生天

582
01:27:49,660 --> 01:27:55,650
患病的人类 肯定就是从这里逃走的
Sick humans must have escaped down here!

583
01:27:59,400 --> 01:28:05,750
不 不！别爬！
No, no! No, no climb! No!

584
01:28:18,530 --> 01:28:21,990
什么？你看到了什么？
What? What you see?

585
01:28:28,120 --> 01:28:30,910
我们在哪里
Wonder where we are.

586
01:28:29,970 --> 01:28:32,970
猿灾

587
01:28:29,970 --> 01:28:32,970
泛滥

588
01:28:54,700 --> 01:28:57,750
不！朋友
No! Friend...

589
01:29:01,060 --> 01:29:05,410
不！
No!

590
01:29:05,410 --> 01:29:07,610
不！不！
No! No!

591
01:29:07,610 --> 01:29:10,320
不！回来 回来！
No! Come, come!

592
01:29:13,780 --> 01:29:17,010
回来！回来 回来
Come! Come, come.

593
01:29:17,010 --> 01:29:18,990
不！回来！
No! Come!

594
01:29:18,990 --> 01:29:21,700
回来！回来！
Come! Come, come!

595
01:29:53,080 --> 01:29:55,790
科巴...
Koba...

596
01:30:00,090 --> 01:30:02,320
睡吧
Sleep.

597
01:30:02,320 --> 01:30:05,570
你救不了他们的
You cannot save them.

598
01:30:06,620 --> 01:30:10,890
猿类都将死在这里
Apes all die here.

599
01:30:13,230 --> 01:30:15,960
- 不会的！- 会的
- No! - Yes.

600
01:30:17,750 --> 01:30:20,560
跟我来...
Join me...

601
01:30:37,280 --> 01:30:39,990
如果明早他还活着
If he's still alive in the morning...

602
01:30:44,630 --> 01:30:48,320
就让他回去和其他猿类一起干活
He goes back to work as everyone else.

603
01:30:48,320 --> 01:30:50,870
不然就杀了他
Or you shoot him.

604
01:30:50,870 --> 01:30:54,860
快来 快来 快来
Come. Come. Come.

605
01:30:57,510 --> 01:31:00,220
她进去了！
She go in!

606
01:32:06,790 --> 01:32:10,290
渴吗？
Thirsty?

607
01:34:25,880 --> 01:34:29,920
躲起来 快点
Hide. Quick.

608
01:34:38,580 --> 01:34:41,610
那些人类会杀了她的！
Humans will kill her!

609
01:34:42,210 --> 01:34:45,430
我知道怎么做 你们快走！
I know what to do! Go!

610
01:36:17,600 --> 01:36:20,310
还有其他猿类在这吗？
Are there others out there?

611
01:36:27,220 --> 01:36:29,930
去搜查下附近
Sweep the area.

612
01:36:29,980 --> 01:36:32,690
把他押到围栏里去
Put him in the pen.

613
01:37:14,330 --> 01:37:18,900
好点了吗？
Feeling better?

614
01:37:23,110 --> 01:37:29,060
那就好 那我们可以计划下逃跑的事了
Good. Then we can talk about escape.

615
01:37:29,070 --> 01:37:32,170
猩猩团结力量大！
Apes together strong!

616
01:37:40,460 --> 01:37:43,860
- 我们既是开始！ - 亦是终结！
- We are the beginning! - And the end!

617
01:38:06,860 --> 01:38:09,570
还活着呢
Still alive.

618
01:38:40,050 --> 01:38:42,920
派他去采石场 就他一个
Send him to the quarry. Alone.

619
01:38:45,440 --> 01:38:48,220
等等
Hold on.

620
01:39:05,720 --> 01:39:08,430
这是什么？
What is this?

621
01:39:11,630 --> 01:39:14,340
这东西怎么到这的？
How did this get in there?

622
01:39:16,520 --> 01:39:19,230
带他去干活
